value.name: Triton's Odoy, Pingree's Silacci named Moynihan Lumber Student-Athletes of the Month
value.description: and the top honoree was senior cross country standout Sarah Harrington, who received the department's highest honor in the Triton Scholar Athlete Award. The award is given to a two-sport athlete ...

value.name: Local Roundup: Newburyport, Triton track split thrilling twilight meet
value.description: Sarah Harrington (11:59.6) and Grace Sousa went 1-2 in the 2-mile and then Aleyo Amasa-Titus (28.4) won the 200, giving the Vikings enough of a cushion to survive Newburyport's win in the 4x400.
